[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71464] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 8: <<pre>>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71466] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 9: <The docs here were copied from Google's Gemini, when I asked it how to generate a cpanfile>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71468] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 10: <**1. Manual Creation**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71470] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 11: <* **Create a file named `cpanfile`:** This file will reside in the root directory of your project.>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71472] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 12: <* **Add dependencies:**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71473] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 13: <* Each line in the `cpanfile` represents a dependency.>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71475] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 14: <* Use the following syntax: `require 'ModuleName';`>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71477] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 15: <* Example>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71478] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 16: <```perl>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71480] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 17: <require 'JSON';>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71482] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 18: <require 'Template';>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71483] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 19: <require 'DateTime';>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71485] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 20: <require 'DBIx::Class';>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71487] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 21: <```>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71488] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 22: <**2. Using `Mojolicious::Command::Author::generate::cpanfile`**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71490] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 23: <* **Install the Mojolicious framework (if not already installed):**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71492] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 24: <```bash>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71493] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 25: <cpanm Mojolicious>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71495] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 26: <```>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71497] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 27: <* **Generate the `cpanfile`:**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71498] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 28: <```bash>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71500] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 29: <mojo generate cpanfile>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71502] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 30: <```>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71504] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 31: <This command analyzes your Perl source code files (usually located in the `lib` directory) to identify used modules and generates the `cpanfile` accordingly.>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71505] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 32: <**3. Using Carton**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71507] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 33: <* **Install Carton:**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71509] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 34: <```bash>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71510] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 35: <cpanm Carton>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71512] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 36: <```>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71514] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 37: <* **Create a `cpanfile`:**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71515] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 38: <```bash>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71517] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 39: <carton init>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71519] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 40: <```>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71520] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 41: <This creates a basic `cpanfile` with some default settings. You can then manually add your project's specific dependencies.>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71522] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 42: <**Key Considerations**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71524] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 43: <* **Version Constraints:** You can specify version constraints for your dependencies to ensure compatibility and stability. For example>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71525] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 44: <```perl>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71527] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 45: <require 'Module::Name' => '>= 1.2.3';>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71529] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 46: <```>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71530] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 47: <* **Local Modules:** If you have local modules that are not on CPAN, you can add them to your `cpanfile` using special directives.>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71532] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 48: <* **Testing:** After generating your `cpanfile`, always test your application to ensure all dependencies are installed correctly and your application functions as expected.>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71534] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 49: <**Example `cpanfile`**>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71535] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 50: <```perl>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71537] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 51: <require 'JSON';>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71538] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 52: <require 'Template' => '>= 2.18';>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71540] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 53: <require 'DateTime';>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71542] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 54: <require 'DBIx::Class';>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71543] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 55: <require 'MyLocalModule'; # A hypothetical local module>. token: 
[2026-06-13 17:03:26.71545] [1390146] [debug] Processing line 56: <```>. token: 
